2010-06-22 16:51:14 UTC - [11]Original Post

   Agree.  Certainly too trivial to clutter the userʼs attention with.
   I changed it to every 30 minutes.
   If I increased it to every 10 minutes, it would still be a small enough
   presence in the log file.  Question is whether that would be more
   output than the user wants when they grep.
